        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="col1" value="✅ DONE — origin/master · deployed · verified" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=14;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;opacity=60;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="40" y="110" width="560" height="900" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="c1" value="&lt;b&gt;commit 33a4e7d&lt;/b&gt; — Least-privilege refactor&#xa;&#xa;• EnableUserLookup toggle added&#xa;• User.ReadWrite.All removed from requiredResourceAccess&#xa;• 6 narrow Graph permissions, 1-to-1 with feature toggles&#xa;• Sentinel labels gained labelType:&quot;User&quot;&#xa;• CRITICAL → High severity mapping&#xa;• Cross-RG workspaceResourceId fix (3-param resourceId)&#xa;• Entra credentials conditionally required" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="70" y="160" width="500" height="180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="c2" value="&lt;b&gt;commit 4dd0535&lt;/b&gt; — v1.1.0 release + ARM URL fix&#xa;&#xa;• FunctionApp.zip (23K) attached to v1.1.0 release&#xa;• ARM WEBSITE_RUN_FROM_PACKAGE → v1.1.0&#xa;• Customer &quot;Deploy to Azure&quot; button now works&#xa;  (v1.0.0 never actually existed on GitHub)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="70" y="360" width="500" height="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="c3" value="&lt;b&gt;commit ac1eb6a&lt;/b&gt; — Force MFA Re-registration&#xa;&#xa;• EnableForceMfaReregistration toggle (OFF by default)&#xa;• actions/entra_id.force_mfa_reregistration()&#xa;• 7 method types: Authenticator, phone, FIDO2,&#xa;  software OATH, Windows Hello, email, TAP&#xa;• Password method always preserved&#xa;• 401/403 graceful permission-denied handling&#xa;• Required: UserAuthenticationMethod.ReadWrite.All" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="70" y="520" width="500" height="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="c4" value="&lt;b&gt;commit cf83299&lt;/b&gt; — Tests&#xa;&#xa;• 7 mock-based unit tests (unittest.mock, no network)&#xa;• 7/7 PASS · CI-safe&#xa;• scripts/test_actions.py test_13 added (live integration,&#xa;  destructive, --run-destructive flag, default off)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="70" y="740" width="500" height="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="col2" value="⏸ BLOCKED — admin action required" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=14;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;opacity=60;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="620" y="110" width="560" height="900" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="b1" value="&lt;b&gt;#7 — Remove lingering broad grant&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;&#xa;SP:   b7d1f4b7-9870-4102-bd73-ffbb507fb95e&#xa;Role: t_TRt3CYAkG9c_-7UH-5Xvv640PPP01FnrhKGGT-XAo&#xa;Perm: User.ReadWrite.All&#xa;&#xa;Needs: Privileged Role Admin or Global Admin&#xa;Current account: Authorization_RequestDenied&#xa;&#xa;az rest --method DELETE --url &quot;https://graph...&quot;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="650" y="160" width="500" height="210" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="b2" value="&lt;b&gt;#5 — Rerun action tests with narrow perms only&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;&#xa;python3 scripts/test_actions.py --skip-ropc&#xa;&#xa;Proves narrow permissions are sufficient on their own.&#xa;Until #7 clears, broad grant silently satisfies calls,&#xa;masking the narrow-only behavior." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="650" y="400" width="500" height="160" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="b3" value="&lt;b&gt;Force MFA — live E2E test&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;&#xa;Needs:&#xa;1. Grant UserAuthenticationMethod.ReadWrite.All app&#xa;   permission + admin consent&#xa;2. Assign Privileged Authentication Administrator&#xa;   directory role to the SP&#xa;3. Disposable test user with registered MFA methods&#xa;4. python3 scripts/test_actions.py --run-destructive&#xa;&#xa;Mock tests already PASS (7/7)." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="650" y="590" width="500" height="230" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="b_edge" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;html=1;endArrow=classic;strokeColor=#856404;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="b1" target="b2">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="b_edge2" value="also unlocks" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;html=1;endArrow=classic;strokeColor=#856404;dashed=1;exitX=1;exitY=0.7;entryX=1;entryY=0;fontSize=10;fontStyle=2;" edge="1" parent="1" source="b1" target="b3">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="col3" value="📋 PENDING — awaiting your decision" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=14;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;opacity=60;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1200" y="110" width="560" height="900" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p1" value="&lt;b&gt;Option 2 — MSSP Multi-Tenant&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;&#xa;Convert app reg to AzureADMultipleOrgs so one&#xa;integration can act on multiple customer tenants&#xa;(A manages X, Y).&#xa;&#xa;Changes:&#xa;• signInAudience = AzureADMultipleOrgs&#xa;• TENANT_MAPPING env var (domain → tenant_id)&#xa;• Per-tenant token cache in function_app.py&#xa;• target_tenant_id column in LAW records&#xa;• scripts/setup_multitenant_app.sh (new)&#xa;&#xa;Blockers:&#xa;• 3 product questions open (defaults proposed)&#xa;• Needs a second disposable Entra tenant for E2E&#xa;&#xa;Effort: 1–2 sessions + 2-tenant E2E test" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1230" y="160" width="500" height="440" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p2" value="&lt;b&gt;GitHub Actions auto-release (nice-to-have)&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;&#xa;Workflow on tag push:&#xa;• zips production/FunctionApp/&#xa;• attaches to a new GitHub release&#xa;• ARM URL pins to /releases/latest/download/&#xa;&#xa;Avoids the stale-URL bug that hit v1.0.0." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1230" y="620" width="500" height="180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
